{
  "stem": "2620.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then McDonnell Douglas-- then Douglas Aircraft got into financial trouble, so they merged with McDonnell from St.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Louis.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's when it became McDonnell Douglas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I stayed there until I retired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, of course, I started dating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always used to love to dance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I do-- I used to go ballroom dancing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's where I met my ex-wife.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got married in December of 1957.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes-- one daughter from that marriage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my daughter is now married, happily married.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's got a good husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He is from Canada.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they have a 9-year-old boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name is Jason Helen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My daughter's name is Karen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They live in the Valley, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That brings us up to-- pretty much to date, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kept me going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what kept me going is that you-- one thing you had to do is you had to have hope that some day this is gonna come to an end.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because once you have nothing to hope for, then you have nothing to live for.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you'll-- you just fall apart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're a goner.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I kept that hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Yeah. 'Cause I-- I've seen-- I've seen people-- strong, big people-- and once they gave up hope, they-- they-- they're gone.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They fell apart.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
